milestones.description: McMillan and Gary Kirsten's 92-run partnership is SA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 91 between Hansie Cronje and Jonty Rhodes
This is the highest match aggregate (472) involving teams South Africa & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Andy Flower has broken the record for most ODIs (18) as captain for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton
